# Cat laser toy for Raspberry PI

Random laser movement to keep cats entertained.

## Testing

Either run laser.py or run manual.py to manually control servos.


## Running on Pi startup

Run the python script on startup by setting it as a cron with `crontab -e`:

```
@reboot /usr/bin/python3 ~/pi-cat-laser/laser.py > ~/pi-cat-laser/out.log 2>&1
```
